Vending machine drinks function as X-items
    Fresh Water -> Guard Spec
    Protein Drink -> X Attack
    Veggie Smoothie -> X Defense
    Lemonade -> X Special Attack
    Moo Moo Milk -> X Special Defense
    Soda Pop -> X Speed
    Canned Coffee -> Dire Hit

Vending machine snacks function as consumable held items
    Focus Band
    Eject Button
    Eject Pack
    Blunder Policy
    Weakness Policy
    Power Herb
    White Herb
    Mental Herb
    Mirror Herb
    Red Card
    Gems
    Room Service
    Beserk Gene

Herbal medicine being much more prominent
    Potions and revives still available
    Otherwise all herbal medicines with their substitutes being rare if available at all

